WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.669
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.669 --> 00:00:03.589
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:03.851 --> 00:00:08.800
It's just me today, but I'm excited to be here, and I pray you are too.

00:00:10.053 --> 00:00:18.400
Yesterday, when Diana and I were praying over the things the Lord had for us, it was over the top.

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:22.743
The presence of the Lord was tangible in this house.

00:00:23.406 --> 00:00:33.040
The Lord showed me again one last call; His eyes were looking over the horizon at the sheep that were lost.

00:00:33.715 --> 00:00:37.280
He would leave the 99 and go after the one.

00:00:37.680 --> 00:00:45.699
I could see Him longing for His lost child, the lost ones, the wayward people in the backfields.

00:00:47.599 --> 00:00:49.200
He's coming for you.

00:00:49.474 --> 00:00:57.719
I believe even Braden loved it when the Lord said, "The devil came at the youth hard, but I'm going to come at them harder.

00:00:57.719 --> 00:01:01.223
I'm coming for the youth of this generation.

00:01:01.223 --> 00:01:11.067
" He said, "I'm coming back for a glorious church," but man, what the Lord has in store for the youth!

00:01:11.413 --> 00:01:21.840
I believe we're about to see some of the greatest moves of the Spirit of the Lord we've ever seen before—demonstrations and manifestations of the glory of God.

00:01:22.040 --> 00:01:24.880
I know the Bible says there's a great falling away.

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:28.336
I understand that, but I know what He also said to me.

00:01:28.336 --> 00:01:31.680
He said, "Brandon, I'm coming for the one.

00:01:33.070 --> 00:01:37.680
" Do you realize how much Jesus loves you today?

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:41.680
Do you realize how much He has a plan for your life?

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:44.340
Every single one of you, He loves.

00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:57.074
When we go through a major city and I see all the people, I think, "Isn't it amazing that He has interest in every single one of us?

00:01:57.074 --> 00:01:59.371
" There are millions and billions of us.

00:01:59.371 --> 00:02:05.016
There are only 300-some million people in the United States; around the world, there are billions.

00:02:05.610 --> 00:02:06.502
Think about that.

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:11.960
He has a plan, and He knows every hair on your head.

00:02:11.960 --> 00:02:17.314
He knows your past, He knows your future, and He knows everything about you.

00:02:17.314 --> 00:02:25.394
He knows the day you're going to take your last breath, but He wants every one of you to know Him.

00:02:25.783 --> 00:02:26.560
That's exciting.

00:02:27.589 --> 00:02:34.360
It's overwhelming to me to think that He has a plan for every single one of us and that He knows us all that well.

00:02:34.360 --> 00:02:39.885
He knows all our faults and our pains; He knows what you're bad at and what you're good at.

00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:42.284
It's amazing.

00:02:42.284 --> 00:02:43.796
God is a good God.

00:02:44.098 --> 00:02:44.760
I was excited.

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:47.211
A lot of people say, "What does Sooner mean?

00:02:47.211 --> 00:02:48.034
" or "What did you see, Sooner?

00:02:49.406 --> 00:02:53.924
" I believe it is a representation of the land run.

00:02:54.653 --> 00:03:05.840
If you look at what the Sooners do—the same reason why they named the college the Oklahoma Sooners—He highlighted "Sooners" in an arch before me.

00:03:06.320 --> 00:03:16.735
He was talking about Japan and South Korea, and I thought that was interesting because He highlighted that to me.

00:03:19.886 --> 00:03:21.706
People say, "How do you see all this?

00:03:21.706 --> 00:03:24.559
Oh, you just have a great imagination, Brandon.

00:03:24.559 --> 00:03:28.400
" I'm not that good, I'll be real with y'all.

00:03:28.400 --> 00:03:33.943
If you realized who is talking to you behind the camera, you would go, "Wow.

00:03:33.943 --> 00:03:43.075
" Seriously, I think it's amazing the things the Lord will show us in prayer if you seek Him.

00:03:43.470 --> 00:03:48.990
When He talked about Iraq again, people say, "Well, are you talking about the revaluation of the Iraqi dinar?

00:03:48.990 --> 00:03:50.373
" I have no idea.

00:03:51.467 --> 00:04:02.789
When I'm in the Spirit like that and saying what I'm seeing, I don't remember a lot of what I'm saying because I'm flowing with the Holy Ghost.

00:04:03.059 --> 00:04:18.035
So my son and my wife will say, "This is what you said," because Diana or Braden takes notes of everything the Lord shows me whenever I'm praying; that's what we do in our private time.

00:04:18.417 --> 00:04:26.000
We're just doing more private time in public view so people can see us and how the Lord flows.

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:28.799
This is what we do on a day-to-day basis.

00:04:28.799 --> 00:04:31.268
This is how serious we take it.

00:04:31.268 --> 00:04:34.080
The Holy Spirit visits us like this all the time.

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:36.788
I'm not bragging; it's just real.

00:04:38.640 --> 00:04:40.453
He will show us that which is to come.

00:04:40.453 --> 00:04:43.460
This is how the Trump ear prophecy came out.

00:04:43.460 --> 00:04:56.640
This is how saying there would be a red wave or XRP, and all these things He's showing me about wars and the plague—it is all birthed out of prayer.

00:05:00.011 --> 00:05:04.863
I don't just walk around and get these prophetic words.

00:05:04.863 --> 00:05:09.973
I told you, I don't feel like I walk in a prophetic gift; I'm a watchman.

00:05:10.360 --> 00:05:14.969
It's totally different than somebody who walks around saying, "I hear the voice of the Lord.

00:05:15.224 --> 00:05:23.760
" That's amazing when it happens, don't get me wrong, but I see when I pray in the Spirit, not in English.

00:05:25.884 --> 00:05:30.208
Even my kids say, "Dad prays in tongues and Dad prays a lot in tongues, and that's what we do.

00:05:30.208 --> 00:05:34.091
" I get in the car and drive around, and the Lord shows me things: open-eyed visions.

00:05:34.091 --> 00:05:38.610
I don't close my eyes when I'm driving around and run into somebody!

00:05:39.780 --> 00:05:43.566
I'm praying and looking, and all of a sudden, He'll show me an open-eyed vision.

00:05:43.840 --> 00:05:47.013
I'll see things, and the Lord will show me that which is to come.

00:05:47.182 --> 00:05:48.600
I believe that's a gift.

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:54.560
I believe God gives those gifts to intercessory prayer people—people who intercede for the nations.

00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:57.188
They intercede and are prayer people.

00:05:57.462 --> 00:06:01.704
I believe that He's no respecter of persons; what He'll do for me, He'll do for you.

00:06:01.704 --> 00:06:09.849
I say it all the time: "Father, give me eyes to see what I need to see and ears for what I need to hear.

00:06:09.849 --> 00:06:14.549
" I thank You, Lord, that I am never snared by any satanic or demonic force.

00:06:14.549 --> 00:06:22.959
I thank You, Father, that no weapon formed against me will prosper, but I hear Your voice, and a stranger's voice I will not follow.

00:06:22.959 --> 00:06:29.951
I hear You, Father; You speak to me and show me that which is to come as I sit on the wall.

00:06:30.255 --> 00:06:31.472
That's what I do.

00:06:31.776 --> 00:06:39.759
I confess that over myself all the time: I hear and see what the Father wants me to see.

00:06:39.759 --> 00:06:41.040
And I take communion.

00:06:41.040 --> 00:06:45.440
I have these communion cups—we've got communion everywhere: the living room, the kitchen, the bedrooms.

00:06:49.660 --> 00:06:51.459
We have it in the car.

00:06:51.759 --> 00:06:55.876
We go before the Lord with communion all the time.

00:07:03.304 --> 00:07:08.594
We like it so much, I told y'all I'm turning purple!

00:07:08.594 --> 00:07:13.019
It's just funny to us because we say we're turning purple.

00:07:13.019 --> 00:07:18.777
Billy Burke says that: "I turn purple, I turn purple," because we take communion so much.

00:07:20.275 --> 00:07:22.479
We believe in the anointing and the power of the Holy Spirit.

00:07:33.880 --> 00:07:34.240
We believe Jesus Christ has chosen us and we are called to the kingdom for such a time as this.

00:07:46.959 --> 00:07:47.199
We're excited you're here.

00:07:47.199 --> 00:07:53.680
We're believing for a million-man and woman prayer army to pray on this channel, as He told us.

00:07:53.680 --> 00:08:02.670
He said, "Brandon, you do this and we can change the course of governments and things all around us.

00:08:12.160 --> 00:08:12.453
" So we saw about that yesterday.

00:08:12.453 --> 00:08:17.360
We saw the Sooners and the things we prayed about Iraq.

00:08:25.813 --> 00:08:26.462
I told you about the attacks; I said we're praying against attacks against our bases—our army bases and naval bases in Iraq.

00:08:26.462 --> 00:08:30.560
I'm not familiar with them, but I saw bases being targets for war.

00:08:31.040 --> 00:08:43.066
So we pray against that and for the Houthis, that they will not be able to hurt any of our service people, that they're always in the right place at the right time, and no weapon formed against them will prosper.

00:08:45.742 --> 00:08:46.000
We pray over that.

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:53.657
I've prayed over what the Lord showed me about Kim Jong-un, the troops going over in the train, and the war trying to escalate.

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:04.340
I see it.

00:09:04.340 --> 00:09:05.760
Then we were praying over...

00:09:05.760 --> 00:09:07.226
there was a lot.

00:09:16.559 --> 00:09:19.280
We had our list, but I thought, "Well, what's fresh today?

00:09:19.280 --> 00:09:22.340
" If the Lord shows us something today, cool.

00:09:22.340 --> 00:09:31.340
If he doesn't, I always go with anticipation that God is going to show up and show off and show us what he wants us to see.

00:09:31.340 --> 00:09:33.920
So, we pray you're excited.

00:09:35.040 --> 00:09:38.354
We pray you want to be a part of this.

00:09:44.365 --> 00:09:44.628
And let's just get started.

00:09:44.628 --> 00:09:53.239
So, we always take communion to start off.

00:09:53.239 --> 00:10:01.698
I always enter by the blood of the Lamb, by the word of our testimony.

00:10:11.880 --> 00:10:12.250
Thank you, Father, for all that you've done.

00:10:21.080 --> 00:10:24.384
Thank you, Father, for all that you've done for us.

00:10:24.384 --> 00:10:30.160
I thank you, God, that you set us free by the blood.

00:10:41.759 --> 00:10:42.079
You said you were wounded for our transgressions.

00:10:44.060 --> 00:10:44.390
You were bruised for our iniquities.

00:10:44.720 --> 00:10:49.371
The chastisement of our peace was upon you.

00:10:51.227 --> 00:10:51.742
And with your stripes, we are healed.

00:10:56.439 --> 00:10:57.040
And Father, we thank you, Lord, for your body that was broken for us today.

00:10:58.530 --> 00:11:03.400
And we take this body and we thank you, Lord, that by your stripes, we are healed.

00:11:08.542 --> 00:11:10.617
And we take it right now in the name of Jesus.

00:11:10.617 --> 00:11:15.479
And we are healed from the top of our head to the soles of our feet.

00:11:20.159 --> 00:11:22.171
And we're expecting the manifestation of what we've been believing for now in Jesus' name.

00:11:22.171 --> 00:11:26.120
Father, we thank you, Lord, that we're delivered.

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:28.080
We're delivered from all bondage.

00:11:28.080 --> 00:11:29.679
We're delivered in Jesus' name.

00:11:29.679 --> 00:11:33.983
And we thank you, Father, for it.

00:11:37.298 --> 00:11:44.959
Lord, we plead the blood of Jesus over us.

00:11:45.359 --> 00:11:58.959
You said in your word, if we confess our sin, you're faithful and just to forgive us of our sin and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

00:12:01.526 --> 00:12:04.903
And we plead the blood of Jesus over us today, God.

00:12:04.903 --> 00:12:12.346
And we thank you, Lord, for we make much of the blood, and the blood will make much of us.

00:12:26.853 --> 00:12:27.107
And we plead the blood of Jesus Christ over us today.

00:12:27.107 --> 00:12:32.275
And we thank you, Father, that it is well with us in our soul.

00:12:46.919 --> 00:12:47.219
And we come up higher with the fire.

00:12:50.129 --> 00:12:58.510
And we see from an eagle's eye, not down on the lower level, but Father, we come up higher with you on the higher level, seated with you in the heavenlies.

00:13:01.394 --> 00:13:01.725
And we take our seat.

00:13:01.725 --> 00:13:05.623
We take our rightful place with you right now in the name of Jesus.

00:13:11.540 --> 00:13:15.600
And we thank you, Lord, that you're making intercession for us at the right hand of the Father.

00:13:22.559 --> 00:13:23.039
And we take this blood right now and we plead the blood of Jesus Christ over us.

00:13:36.906 --> 00:13:37.319
And we thank you, Father, that what you bore in your body, we don't have to bear in our own.

00:13:37.319 --> 00:13:43.053
We're healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

00:13:43.053 --> 00:13:48.400
And we thank you, Father, for all that you've done for us.

00:13:48.400 --> 00:13:51.177
Thank you for your blood.

00:13:51.177 --> 00:13:54.468
Thank you, Lord, for what you've done.

00:13:54.468 --> 00:13:56.685
Glory to your name, Lord.

00:13:56.685 --> 00:14:00.444
We're expecting and we'll be used by you.

00:14:00.444 --> 00:14:05.325
We'll be filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost because we say yes.

00:14:05.325 --> 00:14:11.044
Just like yesterday, he said, 'Who will say yes?

00:14:11.044 --> 00:14:12.800
' We say yes.

00:14:12.800 --> 00:14:14.360
We say yes today, Lord.

00:14:25.371 --> 00:14:25.749
In Jesus' name.

00:14:30.559 --> 00:14:30.879
Lord, we thank you.

00:14:32.177 --> 00:14:34.914
The news is saying there's a rat in the White House.

00:14:34.914 --> 00:14:37.085
I've heard that before.

00:14:38.663 --> 00:14:39.616
Lord, you warned us about the rat.

00:14:39.616 --> 00:14:45.839
You warned us about the people trying to sabotage and do the things that they're trying to do.

00:14:45.839 --> 00:14:55.310
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that the rats are found and caught in the cages that they need to be in.

00:14:56.994 --> 00:14:58.746
I thank you, Father, that you're exposing the rats.

00:14:58.746 --> 00:15:05.657
You're exposing the people that I've seen that are trying to bring down this government.

00:15:05.657 --> 00:15:11.599
Father, your angels are going before us and they're preparing the way.

00:15:11.599 --> 00:15:19.660
I send them out right now in the name of Jesus from the north, the south, the east, the west.

00:15:38.170 --> 00:15:38.420
We call our angels, Father, to war on our behalf today.

00:15:42.331 --> 00:15:45.853
We thank you, Lord, that your warring angel armies are warring on our behalf.

00:15:50.525 --> 00:15:50.902
Father, you said we will work with them.

00:15:59.006 --> 00:16:00.154
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that we will work with them and we commission them to go forth now in the name of Jesus.

00:16:04.040 --> 00:16:08.284
And we thank you, Lord, that they are bearing us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:16:13.896 --> 00:16:15.860
And I pray over President Trump right now in the name of Jesus that he has great discernment.

00:16:21.670 --> 00:16:29.630
And Father, he will hear you even in the midnight hour of knowing who to put around him, God, that he would know who are the rats and who is there to be trusted, Father.

00:16:29.630 --> 00:16:37.779
That he'll not be snared by his own pride or anything of the flesh; that he would hear you, God.

00:16:37.779 --> 00:16:40.200
He would be humbled before you, Father.

00:16:53.920 --> 00:16:54.220
That he would humble himself underneath the mighty hand.

00:16:58.810 --> 00:16:59.016
And in due time, he will be exalted.

00:16:59.633 --> 00:17:02.506
And Lord, he's been exalted into his position of authority over America.

00:17:02.506 --> 00:17:18.346
So Father, I thank you, Lord, that you protect our leader, that you undergird him, Father, that he would have the wisdom to lead this great nation back to victory, Father, delivering us out of the hand of the evil.

00:17:18.346 --> 00:17:27.720
That Father, he is delivered out of the hand of the darkness, that he is not being influenced by any satanic or demonic force.

00:17:27.720 --> 00:17:36.130
I thank you, Lord, for JD Vance, his wife, and his children, and over President Trump, his children, and Melania.

00:17:36.130 --> 00:17:39.680
I pray a hedge of protection around every single one of them.

00:17:39.680 --> 00:17:54.228
Father, I thank you, Lord, for our leaders in Congress and our House, that there will be a radical move of the presence of the Lord, a radical move of the Lord on the Senate and the House floor.

00:17:54.525 --> 00:17:56.260
That we will have revival.

00:17:56.260 --> 00:18:05.600
So, Father, we thank you, Lord, for every judge and every person that's represented in the Congress and in the Senate.

00:18:05.600 --> 00:18:18.770
Father, I pray over them right now in the name of Jesus for making godly laws, that there'll be a supernatural hand of the Holy Ghost on our nation once again for one last call.

00:18:22.389 --> 00:18:22.697
Father, I thank you, Lord.

00:18:36.811 --> 00:18:37.097
I know that you showed me a great financial crash, but Lord, you said to me, 'Brandon, what the prayers prayed in October, the things that were prayed in October, I'm giving you extended time.

00:18:37.097 --> 00:18:46.420
I'm giving you a season of grace for a great wealth transfer will come on the ones that are listening, on the 1%.

00:19:01.980 --> 00:19:05.367
And as they hear me, they will be provided for.

00:19:05.367 --> 00:19:11.816
' There will be a great shaking to awaken over America, for they will be humbled.

00:19:11.816 --> 00:19:14.846
America will be humbled in the days ahead.

00:19:14.846 --> 00:19:19.630
When, I don't know, but Lord, you said it was coming.

00:19:19.630 --> 00:19:25.200
But I know that we will not be caught off guard.

00:19:25.200 --> 00:19:28.142
It's not for us to be caught off guard.

00:19:42.669 --> 00:19:43.057
Father, we pray mercy.

00:19:43.057 --> 00:19:50.800
Just like Abraham interceded on behalf of Sodom and Gomorrah, we intercede on behalf of America.

00:19:53.505 --> 00:20:00.049
And Father, we don't want to not have a shaking to awaken because Father, to keep going down the same road and wanting different results is insanity.

00:20:00.049 --> 00:20:04.789
You have to have something to change it.

00:20:16.057 --> 00:20:16.491
And we thank you, Lord, that there's a changing of the tide.

00:20:16.491 --> 00:20:20.559
There's a changing of circumstances to shake the people out of the slumber.

00:20:22.480 --> 00:20:35.510
And Father, I thank you, Lord, it's not just for the body of Christ, but Father, the ones in the back field, to shake them out of their slumber.

00:20:39.502 --> 00:20:39.866
And what more to do it, Father, than you?

00:20:39.866 --> 00:20:41.250
You'll do this.

00:20:41.830 --> 00:20:58.848
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that this is a time like we've never seen before for the greatest outpouring, the greatest radical outpouring of the Spirit of the Lord, more than what we've ever seen before on this earth, more than any time, more than any other place all throughout eternity.

00:21:03.166 --> 00:21:03.491
Father, we've come to this time, the end of the end.

00:21:07.360 --> 00:21:07.640
And Father, we were born in this time.

00:21:22.030 --> 00:21:22.220
And Father, you've called us for this time.

00:21:23.640 --> 00:21:24.760
And Father, I thank you that we please you.

00:21:34.070 --> 00:21:34.340
You say, 'Well done, thy good and faithful servant.

00:21:34.340 --> 00:21:36.347
Go and enter into my rest.

00:21:36.347 --> 00:21:39.880
' Thank you, Lord, that that's who we are.

00:21:48.640 --> 00:21:52.960
We will be the ones that close this thing up.

00:21:54.091 --> 00:21:54.469
We're the closers.

00:21:54.469 --> 00:22:01.200
Every single one of us right now that are born into this generation are closers.

00:22:02.040 --> 00:22:03.430
And we will be the closers.

00:22:17.460 --> 00:22:17.890
It wasn't brother Hagin.

00:22:17.890 --> 00:22:19.560
It wasn't Oral Roberts.

00:22:19.560 --> 00:22:20.993
It wasn't Kathryn Kuhlman.

00:22:20.993 --> 00:22:24.559
It was us.

00:22:27.889 --> 00:22:28.159
You called us for now.

00:22:28.159 --> 00:22:31.120
They were the generation before the end of all.

00:22:31.960 --> 00:22:34.539
And now you've called us, Lord, and we're going to finish the race.

00:22:34.539 --> 00:22:41.745
They passed the baton, and as they pass the baton, we're running with the relay race baton.

00:22:41.745 --> 00:22:48.600
And we're running and we're going to finish that way.

00:23:03.839 --> 00:23:04.239
We see the finish line ahead of us, Lord, and we want to finish strong.

00:23:06.071 --> 00:23:07.102
We want to live long and finish strong.

00:23:12.667 --> 00:23:17.919
We want to finish the race with great victory and not just barely passing by over that finish line going, "Well, we made it.

00:23:17.919 --> 00:23:20.909
" No, we go running and we break records.

00:23:20.909 --> 00:23:23.263
We're barrier breakers.

00:23:23.263 --> 00:23:30.338
We have a barrier breaker anointing on the inside of us and a barrier breaker mentality.

00:23:30.338 --> 00:23:35.662
We don't have a "just give up, barely getting by" mentality.

00:23:35.662 --> 00:23:42.440
We have a mentality of saying we can do all things through Christ who strengthens us.

00:23:54.880 --> 00:23:55.107
We can do all things, for you've given us strength and a hope.

00:23:55.107 --> 00:23:58.074
I believe, Father, that we'll be the barrier breakers.

00:23:58.074 --> 00:24:13.013
Where Billy Graham went and saved hundreds of thousands in a meeting, Father, it will be more on us: the greater anointing, a greater capacity, a greater revelation of your word.

00:24:29.234 --> 00:24:29.600
Father, I thank you, Lord, for supernatural wisdom concerning the word of God, that we would have an anointing of knowing how to teach and preach the word in a way that no generation has ever done before.

00:24:29.600 --> 00:24:33.475
I thank you, Father, that this is a time that we soar.

00:24:39.245 --> 00:24:39.451
